			<div class="content" id="post-content-738688">
									

<p>Last time someone mentioned Dogpile Irregulars it was to castigate me for leaving such an unfunny joke up on my last comic.</p>
<p>www.elfonlyinn.net</p>
<p>P.S. The joke I had wanted to tell was about a blog I'd heard of called "Lurking Rhythmically" (never read it, don't plan on reading it) which would have triggered a response of "It sounds like you're teabagging the internet." I still think that would have been funnier, but I didn't want to dog on a blog I didn't read.</p>
<p>P.P.S. Bizarrely the author of said blog somehow knew I was thinking of him and sent me a message about it which went unread for months and months.</p>
<p>P.P.P.S. Oh now I remember why the dude knew I was thinking of him, I still threw in an edited version of the blog name. Man that last strip was ass.</p>

